Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.38,0:02:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, the \Nsecond half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.92,0:03:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it \Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.31,0:03:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body \Nturned to rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.02,0:03:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.72,0:03:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After surviving a fierce battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Straw Hats finally \Nentered the New World,--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the harshest sea ruled by the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.04,0:03:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They landed on Punk Hazard; an island with \Ntwo parts, one burning, the other frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After forming an alliance with Trafalgar Law,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.56,0:03:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy finally encountered Caesar Clown
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,aka the Master who rules the island
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.53,0:03:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but was beaten by his mysterious power.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:04:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Law, too, got taken down by \Nthe Navy G-5 base commander - Vergo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you take them away? \NThe children are suffering!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.75,0:04:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.96,0:04:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Bird Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.28,0:04:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.02,0:04:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gastanet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.48,0:04:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Brownbeard!\N--What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gastanet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.95,0:04:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shaking Up the New World! \NCaesar's Horrendous Experiment!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:51.43,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,IN FRONT OF CAESAR'S LABORATORY
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! It's as solid as rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Open the shutter!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.24,0:05:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us back Smo-yan and Tashigi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those creepy creatures...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They went that way but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about them! Focus on saving \NSmo-yan and Tashigi-chan now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open it, Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.33,0:05:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An airship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, get off, children!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.61,0:05:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.74,0:05:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever go out on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.65,0:05:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheep-san, give me the candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master! I want the candy now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My head hurts! Master, give me the candy now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, you can have it soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, go straight \Nback to the Biscuit Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.83,0:06:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've left plenty of candy in there for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.43,0:06:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go back to my research room now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Relax and enjoy the candies in the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are very, very delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.76,0:06:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the room! Show \Nme the way, Mr. Sheep!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's this way, kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.19,0:06:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The Biscuit Room!\N--I want the candy now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.19,0:06:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what to do, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.03,0:06:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once they're all inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.87,0:07:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lock them up securely and \Ndon't ever let them get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.20,0:07:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.10,0:07:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's scary here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.01,0:07:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.29,0:07:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.01,0:07:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.07,0:07:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go back to \Nthe room like everyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.23,0:07:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and have that sweet candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.74,0:07:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.62,0:07:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go! Do you wanna go back to the lab?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.83,0:07:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, give me the candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:08:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it. Come back to me, children.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.89,0:08:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't go back to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.47,0:08:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you wanna go home?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.31,0:08:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1, 2, 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I wanna get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.63,0:08:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold outside and don't you \Nrealize what floor you're on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, go back to the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Help me, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mocha?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.94,0:08:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go get the candy already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good girl! Go back to the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The candy is in that room!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you people so scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared! I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis and the others were very nice to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.90,0:09:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because I'm not a good child?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I didn't listen to you! Bro! Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, get away from the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.48,0:09:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! What a pain in the butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me! Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:32.21,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE REMAINS OF THE FIRST \NAND SECOND LABORATORY
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.81,0:09:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a whole bunch of cuts \Nand bruises on Sanji-kun's body
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's so strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm alive thanks to his body!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:09:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are the children?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:10:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with me, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.58,0:10:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You came to save me, Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.14,0:10:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't be so disappointed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to save the children!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.31,0:10:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.73,0:10:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, just sugar is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to take care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.16,0:10:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.53,0:10:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what's taking Caesar so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.52,0:11:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting, Vergo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem. I was having coffee and cookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.01,0:11:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's odd. The cookies are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't serve you any cookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I wasn't having cookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.94,0:11:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When does the experiment start, Caesar?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.03,0:11:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon. Monet, turn the video on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.09,0:11:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.99,0:11:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I wish you had your man
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.89,0:11:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,under better control, Vergo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.29,0:11:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I saw Smoker here,  \NI broke into a cold sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.92,0:11:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well - he was like a wild \Ndog. He was beyond my control.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.05,0:11:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that'll all change after today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.06,0:12:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.98,0:12:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.36,0:12:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you were quite helpless \Nagainst Vergo! Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.49,0:12:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The deal I had with you worked in my favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.74,0:12:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange for letting you stay here,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.68,0:12:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're going to give my people legs?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.16,0:12:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be nice, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.37,0:12:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But since you're stronger than me
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.85,0:12:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm the boss of this island,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.63,0:12:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you want to stay here, I \Nneed a little bit of insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.93,0:12:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't planning on hurting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.47,0:12:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this, Trafalgar Law?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.10,0:12:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to entrust my dear \Nsecretary Monet's heart to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.82,0:12:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that okay, Monet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.82,0:12:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.03,0:12:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In return,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:13:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let me keep your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's a deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we have each other by the balls,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.44,0:13:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can't do anything bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I feel safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew I shouldn't trust anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your own fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.62,0:13:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you learned it the \Nhard way already but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Vergo has your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it was impossible even for \Na man such as yourself to notice
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Monet tactfully transformed \Nherself and followed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.43,0:13:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you alright?! Tra-guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.10,0:13:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you guys are up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.81,0:14:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a shame, Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we became good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been saved by your \Ndiligent secretary, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should've been more careful about Monet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing as how the "Master" was \Nso dumb, I didn't care much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch your mouth, young man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.33,0:14:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it! He took your \Nheart and you're still alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.04,0:14:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How stupid can you be, letting him \Ntake advantage of your own ability?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.20,0:14:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.76,0:14:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.43,0:14:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.58,0:14:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The video is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.26,0:14:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a lucky man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.10,0:15:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, put it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.49,0:15:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a huge ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.91,0:15:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.47,0:15:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something is on the screen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.51,0:15:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that? Where is it? That looks like...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.58,0:15:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a candy! It's a huge candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.68,0:15:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did they place that \NVideo Transponder Snail?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.61,0:16:22.46,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,VARIOUS PLACES IN THE NEW \NWORLD UNDERWORLD BROKERS
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:09.76,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for waiting, brokers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.76,0:16:13.85,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to start soon. The Smilies...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.85,0:16:15.11,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,...that made their way
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:17.18,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,from the Burning Lands separately...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.18,0:16:19.94,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,...will all arrive at this
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.94,0:16:22.46,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,central part of the Ice Lands very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When they merge into one another
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and become one big "Smiley" again,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.35,0:16:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the experiment will begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see - Smiley is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the H2S poison gas bomb itself...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the same one that killed \Neverything on the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...four years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H2S gas?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.05,0:17:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last time,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.60,0:17:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,despite the fact they were \Ngrowing weaker by the minute,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.58,0:17:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,those afflicted with the gas \Nwere able to take cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:18:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what I'm going to do is give Smiley,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.47,0:18:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the weapon from four \Nyears ago, a big "boost."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will add a new effect to the poison gas
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.11,0:18:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the weapon of mass destruction \Nwill reach completion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The new weapon that will make \Nits debut today is called...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.42,0:18:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Shinokuni!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:22.53,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE ICE LANDS - THE CENTRAL PART
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.67,0:18:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.55,0:18:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we even outrun such monsters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.14,0:18:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It finally coalesced into \None blob on this side!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.15,0:18:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, what is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What difference does it make now?! Just run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.54,0:18:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys! I see a ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.37,0:18:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.12,0:18:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like... a candy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody's there underneath it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.91,0:19:07.37,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,VEGAPUNK'S DRAGON - SMALL SIZE
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.92,0:19:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, I see a big, gel-like creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.01,0:19:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's Smiley.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.19,0:19:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we are going to project Master's \Nvideo on the fog as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.38,0:19:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.70,0:19:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you all have to get out \Nof there. It's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up with the dragon sled...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.94,0:19:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.04,0:19:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a problem! The sled is melting!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.85,0:19:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did it happen? Is it some \Nkind of chemical reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't use it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:19:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dragon escaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.01,0:19:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?! One thing after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.85,0:19:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.45,0:20:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a bit overdramatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You all, just run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.65,0:20:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The protective suit won't help!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.36,0:20:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it off and run to the lab now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.57,0:20:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.54,0:20:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take the suit off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Master is always right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he has a plan! Do as he says!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.55,0:20:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.30,0:20:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope this works right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.65,0:20:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.95,0:20:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody's image is being \Nprojected in the air this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.44,0:20:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about all that crap! Just run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.52,0:21:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smiley! I missed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.69,0:21:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been three years!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.64,0:21:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yes, Smiley?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This brings back memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something good for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.47,0:21:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Wait, Smiley!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.93,0:21:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.39,0:21:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must obey me! Just as I taught you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.81,0:21:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I said "Wait"!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.06,0:21:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a great deal to talk about!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.64,0:21:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.85,0:21:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.00,0:21:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...four years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.57,0:21:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.38,0:21:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, all right! You can eat now! Oh yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.06,0:21:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not listening to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.60,0:22:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.10,0:22:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's acting funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.43,0:22:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.95,0:22:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a big candy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.22,0:22:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good boy, Smiley.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.54,0:23:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody can stop him now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.94,0:23:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Used in the past to convert Punk \NHazard into a land of death,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.38,0:23:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar's ultimate poison is unleashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.28,0:23:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It swallows person after person as it spreads...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.80,0:23:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and closes in on the Straw Hats as the island is transformed into a hellish landscape.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.68,0:23:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.27,0:23:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Deadliest Weapon of Mass \NDestruction in History! Shinokuni!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.44,0:23:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
